{"tid":2274466,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★新聞處聘助理新聞主任起薪3萬 或掀起「爭崩頭」情況","createTime":"2020-11-06T12:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T13:00:06.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"58890009a39766094870f9064f70a4a24f219814","tid":2274466,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:35:17.000Z","msg":"受新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情影響，本港勞工市場情況嚴峻，應屆大學生就有喜訊！政府新聞處今日（6日）起招聘助理新聞主任（一般工作），起薪每月達30,235元，是自2018年後再次招聘此職位。但今次空缺名額只有約10名，或掀起「爭崩頭」情況。<br />\n<br />\n根據入職條件，申請人只須持有香港任何一所大學頒發的學士學位，對修讀的學科則未見有要求；其他條件則包括在綜合招聘考試的能力傾向測試取得及格成績，以及綜合招聘考試的中文及英文試卷取得二級成績，或具備同等成績，就可申請有關職位。招聘網頁亦列明，現正修讀大學學士學位的應屆畢業生亦可申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/545579/%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E7%AD%8D%E5%B7%A5-%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%99%95%E8%81%98%E5%8A%A9%E7%90%86%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E8%B5%B7%E8%96%AA3%E8%90%AC-%E6%87%89%E5%B1%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F545579%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258B%2599%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25AD%258D%25E5%25B7%25A5-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%2599%2595%25E8%2581%2598%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%2596%25AA3%25E8%2590%25AC-%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%25B1%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%258F%25AF%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9nbrkFmDP3UEX6OAVSOiSMc%3D&h=2f1daa55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/545579/%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E5%93%A1%E7%AD%8D%E5%B7%A5-%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%99%95%E8%81%98%E5%8A%A9%E7%90%86%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E8%B5%B7%E8%96%AA3%E8%90%AC-%E6%87%89%E5%B1%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B</a>"},{"pid":"b29bb089c94e13644e91779e7a99c877deb68c55","tid":2274466,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42d0e7702614f13e9093d9a147e2f597895e032","tid":2274466,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:36:03.000Z","msg":"附帶福利則包括有薪假期、醫療及牙科診療；在適當情況下，<span class=\"xx-large\">公務員更可獲得房屋資助</span>。該職位是繼2018年11月展開招聘後，事隔兩年再作招聘。政府新聞處指，有關空缺名額約10名；而2018年的招聘中，共聘請了40多人，即今次名額比上次招聘更少。<br />\n<br />\n助理新聞主任（一般工作）會被派駐在政府新聞處、政府總部新聞組及部門新聞公共關係小組從事有關新聞事務、宣傳及公共關係的工作；職責主要負責大眾傳播研究、統籌新聞發放及傳媒採訪、宣傳、推廣及處理緊急事故的工作。受聘人或須輪班工作。"},{"pid":"c284ce4acb3d177c5f337daaf1ef81437cd539a0","tid":2274466,"uid":56698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:46:31.000Z","msg":"做呢啲工呢真係生仔冇屎窟㗎<br />\n之前已經有個一辭職就被自殺咗啦"},{"pid":"67d65e800d31a01552398429d798530d0c6895fd","tid":2274466,"uid":209024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"做政府發言人？"},{"pid":"d52e6bb9804e239e603b090b3dfef6e37e6197e5","tid":2274466,"uid":331421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:53:37.000Z","msg":"請人要fill返之前自殺果個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a31af7581528d094a8940ee2f30a72c2df4b02","tid":2274466,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"新聞官 肯定請奶共狗架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\